{"tid":2420882,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GD緋聞女友多籮籮 Jennie認戀Kai不足一個月即甩拖","createTime":"2021-02-24T07:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T13:44:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c680f48bb9cbcfbcf5af8d82ac16fd131b11a71e","tid":2420882,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vQKkSlW8JzfxIZXcyGMcQ2A0jZQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TUUKC6UWN5GA7ICP37ZK4NT7CU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvQKkSlW8JzfxIZXcyGMcQ2A0jZQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTUUKC6UWN5GA7ICP37ZK4NT7CU.jpg&h=8b4b7f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國天團BIGBANG的32歲隊長G-DRAGON（GD），今日被爆跟同門師妹女團BLACK PINK的25歲成員Jennie撻着，並公開二人的約會照，不過GD就例牌不承認亦不否認。GD出道以來緋聞多多，先後與水原希子、珠妍等人爆戀情，但他從未公開認戀。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：GD爆新戀情 舊愛珠妍即發圖：要堅強面對<br />\n水原希子<br />\nGD和日本電影《進擊的巨人》的30歲女星水原希子，由2010年開始傳緋聞，二人曾經常斷正被影到秘密旅行、戴情侶飾物，又被偷拍到於首爾深夜甜蜜攬腰摸面，外界都認為二人打風都打唔甩。不過據知二人事業心重，加上經常分隔兩地，最終於2015年傳出分手消息。雖然2016年曾傳二人復合，不過之後他們先後跟其他藝人爆戀情，令「GD &amp; 水原希子」成為過去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XDqpRJX_VwYdfaae88f28obIgns=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/644CD7JW6JDMTOJNEDI3KH7BP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXDqpRJX_VwYdfaae88f28obIgns%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F644CD7JW6JDMTOJNEDI3KH7BP4.jpg&h=750f852a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰妍<br />\nGD跟水原希子被爆分手後，於2015年10月就突然傳出跟女團少女時代（少時）成員泰妍拍拖的傳聞，當時GD方面表示：「冇回應的價值。」不過於2016年就再有網民指GD和泰妍不時借IG傳情，二人的事務所就選擇沉默，未有回應緋聞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DKPhCg4XC_MMGv4CUhEykM-ATxU=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SYCUYXHEZFADDFV7X6AO2HAT7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDKPhCg4XC_MMGv4CUhEykM-ATxU%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSYCUYXHEZFADDFV7X6AO2HAT7A.jpg&h=709468e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fqfk-KlGaMLFAr3FrUp1qQnAtrc=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XTT3L3JXYJB7TION6SKRF6Z2PQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffqfk-KlGaMLFAr3FrUp1qQnAtrc%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXTT3L3JXYJB7TION6SKRF6Z2PQ.jpg&h=3da23100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小松菜奈<br />\nGD於2016年爆出跟25歲日本女星小松菜奈的緋聞，二人曾合作拍攝雜誌，之後二人被拍到在日本撐枱腳，又疑似戴上情侶手鏈。隨後GD被爆其私人IG賬號被黑客入侵，流出大量私密照，包括二人在床上晒情侶襪照，不過去年就傳小松菜奈疑戀日本影帝菅田將暉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/46lhNbR6d146swjyt8WjLQsWhbk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TBU6QFXT7BCRTJMLFI2KVKIQXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F46lhNbR6d146swjyt8WjLQsWhbk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTBU6QFXT7BCRTJMLFI2KVKIQXU.jpg&h=5412c96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSulli<br />\nGD於2017年曾傳跟已故女星、女團f(x)前成員Sulli拍拖，當時Sulli跟GD一齊去遊樂場玩，又被指戴同款心型戒指，GD方面否認戀情，又指二人孖一班朋友去完遊樂場後，就沒有再見面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/To65Z5Qn_lPgMHtZXEDMkGubEnc=/802x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EGKOOHN7P5AWBNXUDEYEA77G5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTo65Z5Qn_lPgMHtZXEDMkGubEnc%3D%2F802x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEGKOOHN7P5AWBNXUDEYEA77G5U.jpg&h=381666d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jptYLwuY5-ugW9R4sGXzfG_6WPw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2JKJ3ELNDFEHJKPD7GR5UGUVGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjptYLwuY5-ugW9R4sGXzfG_6WPw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2JKJ3ELNDFEHJKPD7GR5UGUVGQ.jpg&h=f5ca41a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珠妍<br />\nGD跟蘇志燮緋聞女友、女團After School的33歲前成員珠妍，於2017年時已傳兩人秘交1年，兩人曾親密頭貼頭玩手機配音App，不過片段流出後珠妍方面強調兩人只是好友。至2018年韓媒《Dispatch》拍得二人同遊濟州的約會照，不過GD一直唔認戀情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EiRSBUI3XDsmZ-yyuVPjfWShPhY=/802x1004/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U2TJBHAZNFD47MEADYEP6NUANU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEiRSBUI3XDsmZ-yyuVPjfWShPhY%3D%2F802x1004%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU2TJBHAZNFD47MEADYEP6NUANU.jpg&h=80cbcad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A_Ntit73i5CmEKbabB9KISqbI9Y=/802x509/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QUTE3LZXCFHWFBAO4D6GE57NHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA_Ntit73i5CmEKbabB9KISqbI9Y%3D%2F802x509%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQUTE3LZXCFHWFBAO4D6GE57NHA.jpg&h=3c8fb6d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x6IrtmObfGuItEDCau8CocH6tCI=/802x1145/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZ6HYZAILNFNZBGXHW2BHXQ4YA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx6IrtmObfGuItEDCau8CocH6tCI%3D%2F802x1145%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZ6HYZAILNFNZBGXHW2BHXQ4YA.jpg&h=23677e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210224/U6YG377KPVERRFWVJONJRMX2VU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210224%2FU6YG377KPVERRFWVJONJRMX2VU%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=0609956c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210224%2FU6YG377KPVERRFWVJONJRMX2VU%2F&h=6fed060a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210224/U6YG377KPVERRFWVJONJRMX2VU/</a>"},{"pid":"f60e7dc6ae48e9139f017a3249ca44a865b5bf95","tid":2420882,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"Jennie曾認戀Kai<br />\n至於Jennie，出道後曾認戀EXO的Kai。Jennie於前年元旦日遭《Dispatch》踢爆戀情，公開二人於公園甜蜜約會的照片，當時雙方大方認愛。不過戀情見光死，二人認戀不到1個月就宣佈分手。前年11月有網民猜測二人其實是轉玩地下情，不過雙方沒有回應傳聞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pweFQez68d1_Mq9hncGOoTOdt9c=/802x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NZKABDGSIBCL7AOVEWLOIUS45Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpweFQez68d1_Mq9hncGOoTOdt9c%3D%2F802x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNZKABDGSIBCL7AOVEWLOIUS45Q.jpg&h=bf23f808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0abe1c7ea263c57a7ee14214e29f7bc07278d2b8","tid":2420882,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"Kai比人玩到臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i